snippet.title: Amber Heard’s Lawyer Exposes Her For Destroying Johnny Depp & Quits
snippet.description:
Amber's Lawyer Exposes Her For Destroying Johnny Depp & Quits
----------
Amber Heard and Johnny Depp's divorce has been a surprise to the public, and now it's
been several years of a legal battle with no end in sight. Things later took a surprising turn as Amber Heard's credibility was questioned; her lawyer exposed her for destroying Johnny Depp and quit afterward. So what exactly is going on in this case?
